{"word":"G1252 - διακρίνω - diakrínō - dee-ak-ree'-no - Contend","slug":"G1252","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διακρίνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>diakrínō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>dee-ak-ree'-no"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Contend"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B4;&#x03B9;&#x03B1;&#x03BA;&#x03C1;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03BD;&#x03C9; - diakrino&#x0304;</b> - <i>dee-ak-ree'-no</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G2919\">G2919</a>; to <i>separate thoroughly</i>, that is, (literally and reflexively) to <i>withdraw</i> from, or (by implication) <i>oppose</i>; figuratively to <i>discriminate</i> (by implication <i>decide</i>), or (reflexively) <i>hesitate:</i> - contend, make (to) differ (-ence), discern, doubt, judge, be partial, stagger, waver."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1253\">G1253</a>, <a href=\"#/G1469\">G1469</a>, <a href=\"#/G178\">G178</a>, <a href=\"#/G2631\">G2631</a>, <a href=\"#/G2632\">G2632</a>, <a href=\"#/G2633\">G2633</a>, <a href=\"#/G2917\">G2917</a>, <a href=\"#/G2919\">G2919</a>, <a href=\"#/G2920\">G2920</a>, <a href=\"#/G2922\">G2922</a>, <a href=\"#/G2923\">G2923</a>, <a href=\"#/G2924\">G2924</a>, <a href=\"#/G350\">G350</a>, <a href=\"#/G351\">G351</a>, <a href=\"#/G470\">G470</a>, <a href=\"#/G610\">G610</a>, <a href=\"#/G611\">G611</a>, <a href=\"#/G612\">G612</a>, <a href=\"#/G843\">G843</a>, <a href=\"#/G87\">G87</a>"}]}